<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>FUCK.repair — Fix Anything</title>
  <meta
    name="description"
    content="Upload manuals. Learn real repair methods. Share tips and tricks. If it's broken, start here."
  />
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #06070a;
      --bg-2: #0b0d12;
      --panel: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
      --panel-2: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
      --panel-3: rgba(255,255,255,0.02);
      --text: #f5f7fb;
      --muted: #9ca3af;
      --soft: #cfd6e4;
      --line: rgba(255,255,255,0.10);
      --line-2: rgba(255,255,255,0.16);
      --glow: rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
      --max: 1440px;
      --radius: 5px;
      --radius-lg: 5px;
      --shadow:
        0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,0.05) inset,
        0 0 0 1px rgba(255,255,255,0.03),
        0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.45);
      --pad: clamp(20px, 3vw, 40px);
      --display: clamp(3.6rem, 10vw, 8.7rem);
      --h2: clamp(1.9rem, 4vw, 3.2rem);
      --body: clamp(1rem, 1.4vw, 1.08rem);
      --nav: 0.84rem;
      --small: 0.84rem;
    }

    * { box-sizing: border-box; }
    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

    body {
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--text);
      font-family: Inter, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
      text-rendering: optimizeLegibility;
      background:
        radial-gradient(900px 500px at 12% 8%, rgba(255,255,255,0.09), transparent 60%),
        radial-gradient(700px 400px at 88% 12%, rgba(120,160,255,0.08), transparent 55%),
        linear-gradient(180deg, #06070a 0%, #090b10 45%, #06070a 100%);
      background-attachment: fixed;
    }

    body::before {
      content: "";
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      pointer-events: none;
      background:
        linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,0.02), rgba(255,255,255,0.02)) top / 100% 1px no-repeat,
        linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.015), transparent 18%, transparent 82%, rgba(255,255,255,0.015));
      opacity: 0.75;
      mix-blend-mode: screen;
    }

    a { color: inherit; text-decoration: none; }
    img { max-width: 100%; display: block; }

    .wrap {
      width: min(100%, var(--max));
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding-left: var(--pad);
      padding-right: var(--pad);
    }

    .glass {
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--panel), var(--panel-3));
      backdrop-filter: blur(18px) saturate(130%);
      -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(18px) saturate(130%);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    }

    .site-header {
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 100;
      padding-top: 14px;
    }

    .site-header .shell {
      border-radius: 5px;
      min-height: 74px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 22px;
      padding: 0 22px;
    }

    .brand {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
      font-size: 0.92rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.22em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .brand-mark {
      width: 11px;
      height: 11px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 35% 35%, rgba(255,255,255,0.95), rgba(255,255,255,0.24) 60%, rgba(255,255,255,0.08) 100%);
      box-shadow:
        0 0 14px rgba(255,255,255,0.22),
        0 0 30px rgba(140,180,255,0.08);
      flex: 0 0 auto;
    }

    .nav {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 24px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .nav a {
      font-size: var(--nav);
      color: var(--muted);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.16em;
      transition: color 150ms ease, opacity 150ms ease;
    }

    .nav a:hover {
      color: var(--text);
    }

		.button,
button {
  appearance: none;
  border: 1px solid var(--line-2);
  background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.10), rgba(255,255,255,0.04));
  color: var(--text);
  min-height: 50px;
  padding: 0 18px;
  border-radius: 5px;
  font: inherit;
  font-size: 0.82rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.16em;
  cursor: pointer;
  transition:
    transform 140ms ease,
    border-color 140ms ease,
    background 140ms ease,
    box-shadow 140ms ease;
  box-shadow:
    0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,0.06) inset,
    0 10px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.26);

  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  text-align: center;
}

    .button:hover,
    button:hover {
      transform: translateY(-1px);
      border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.26);
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.14), rgba(255,255,255,0.06));
    }

    .button.primary {
      color: #05070a;
      background:
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.98), rgba(225,232,244,0.92));
      border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
      box-shadow:
        0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,0.9) inset,
        0 10px 30px rgba(255,255,255,0.08),
        0 14px 34px rgba(0,0,0,0.26);
    }

    .button.primary:hover {
      background:
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,1), rgba(235,240,248,0.96));
    }

    .hero {
      position: relative;
      padding-top: clamp(40px, 6vw, 70px);
      padding-bottom: clamp(70px, 9vw, 110px);
    }

    .hero-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.08fr 0.92fr;
      gap: clamp(26px, 4vw, 52px);
      align-items: stretch;
    }

    .hero-copy {
      padding: clamp(26px, 4vw, 40px);
      border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
      min-height: 720px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: space-between;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .hero-copy::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      inset: auto -10% -35% auto;
      width: 55%;
      height: 55%;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,255,255,0.09), transparent 68%);
      filter: blur(22px);
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .eyebrow {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      color: var(--soft);
      font-size: 0.76rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.22em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }

    .eyebrow::before {
      content: "";
      width: 34px;
      height: 1px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.30);
      display: inline-block;
    }

    h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: var(--display);
      line-height: 0.9;
      letter-spacing: -0.07em;
      font-weight: 800;
      max-width: 9.5ch;
    }

    .hero-sub {
      margin-top: 24px;
      max-width: 45rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: clamp(1.04rem, 1.7vw, 1.18rem);
      line-height: 1.65;
    }

    .hero-actions {
      display: flex;
      gap: 12px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      margin-top: 34px;
    }

    .hero-metrics {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 14px;
      margin-top: 42px;
    }

    .metric {
      padding: 18px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.05), rgba(255,255,255,0.025));
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.10);
    }

    .metric-kicker {
      display: block;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.72rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.15em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .metric strong {
      display: block;
      font-size: 1rem;
      line-height: 1.35;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .hero-side {
      display: grid;
      gap: 16px;
    }

    .panel {
      border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
      overflow: hidden;
      position: relative;
    }

    .terminal {
      min-height: 720px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .terminal-top {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 18px 22px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.74rem;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.16em;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.03), rgba(255,255,255,0.015));
    }

    .terminal-body {
      padding: 24px 22px 28px;
      font-family: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Consolas, monospace;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: #dfe5ef;
      line-height: 1.72;
      flex: 1;
      position: relative;
    }

    .terminal-body::after {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      inset: auto 0 0 0;
      height: 140px;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, transparent, rgba(6,7,10,0.9));
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .terminal-line {
      display: block;
      white-space: pre-wrap;
    }

    .prompt { color: #ffffff; }
    .muted { color: var(--muted); }
    .ok { color: #e9eef7; }

    .section {
      padding-top: clamp(20px, 2vw, 28px);
      padding-bottom: clamp(20px, 2vw, 28px);
    }

    .section-card {
      border-radius: 34px;
      padding: clamp(26px, 4vw, 40px);
    }

    .section-head {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 0.76fr 1.24fr;
      gap: clamp(24px, 4vw, 60px);
      align-items: start;
      margin-bottom: 34px;
    }

    h2 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: var(--h2);
      line-height: 0.96;
      letter-spacing: -0.05em;
      max-width: 12ch;
    }

    .section-intro {
      max-width: 58rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: var(--body);
      line-height: 1.75;
    }

    .grid-3,
    .grid-4 {
      display: grid;
      gap: 14px;
    }

    .grid-3 { grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); }
    .grid-4 { grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); }

    .card {
      border-radius: 5px;
      padding: 22px;
      min-height: 220px;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.045), rgba(255,255,255,0.02));
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.09);
      box-shadow:
        0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,0.05) inset,
        0 18px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.28);
    }

    .label {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-bottom: 14px;
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      letter-spacing: 0.18em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .card h3 {
      margin: 0 0 12px;
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      line-height: 1.12;
      letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    }

    .card p {
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.65;
      font-size: 0.98rem;
    }

    .manuals-table-wrap {
      border-radius: 5px;
      overflow: hidden;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.09);
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.04), rgba(255,255,255,0.015));
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    }

    .manuals-table {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
    }

    .manuals-table th,
    .manuals-table td {
      text-align: left;
      padding: 18px 16px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
      vertical-align: top;
    }

    .manuals-table th {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.72rem;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.16em;
      font-weight: 700;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02);
    }

    .manuals-table td {
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      color: #edf2f9;
    }

    .manuals-table tr:last-child td { border-bottom: none; }
    .state { font-weight: 700; color: #ffffff; }

    .tip-list {
      display: grid;
      gap: 14px;
    }

    .tip {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 120px 1fr;
      gap: 18px;
      padding: 20px 22px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.035), rgba(255,255,255,0.02));
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    }

    .tip-tag {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.72rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.17em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      padding-top: 4px;
    }

    .tip-copy h4 {
      margin: 0 0 8px;
      font-size: 1.06rem;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    }

    .tip-copy p {
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .upload-panel {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 14px;
    }

    .upload-box {
      border-radius: 5px;
      padding: 26px;
      min-height: 240px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: space-between;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.04), rgba(255,255,255,0.02));
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      box-shadow:
        0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,0.04) inset,
        0 18px 38px rgba(0,0,0,0.25);
    }

    .upload-box h3 {
      margin: 0 0 10px;
      font-size: 1.24rem;
      letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    }

    .upload-box p {
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .input-row {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 12px;
      margin-top: 16px;
    }

    input,
    textarea,
    select {
      width: 100%;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.10);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
      color: var(--text);
      min-height: 52px;
      padding: 12px 16px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      outline: none;
      font: inherit;
      transition: border-color 150ms ease, background 150ms ease, box-shadow 150ms ease;
    }

    textarea {
      min-height: 160px;
      resize: vertical;
    }

    input:focus,
    textarea:focus,
    select:focus {
      border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.22);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.045);
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
    }

    input::placeholder,
    textarea::placeholder {
      color: #7f8694;
    }

    .stat-band {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
      gap: 14px;
    }

    .stat {
      border-radius: 5px;
      padding: 24px;
      min-height: 170px;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.04), rgba(255,255,255,0.02));
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.09);
      box-shadow:
        0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,0.04) inset,
        0 18px 38px rgba(0,0,0,0.25);
    }

    .stat-number {
      font-size: clamp(2.3rem, 4vw, 3.7rem);
      line-height: 0.95;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: -0.05em;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    .stat-copy {
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.6;
      font-size: 0.98rem;
    }

    .cta {
      text-align: center;
    }

    .cta-shell {
      border-radius: 5px;
      padding: clamp(30px, 5vw, 56px);
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .cta-shell::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      inset: -15% auto auto 50%;
      width: 60%;
      height: 60%;
      transform: translateX(-50%);
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,255,255,0.10), transparent 68%);
      filter: blur(18px);
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .cta h2 {
      font-size: clamp(2.3rem, 5vw, 4.8rem);
      max-width: 12ch;
      margin: 0 auto 18px;
      line-height: 0.92;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }

    .cta p {
      max-width: 46rem;
      margin: 0 auto 26px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      line-height: 1.75;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }

    .cta-row {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 12px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }

    .site-footer {
      padding-top: 18px;
      padding-bottom: 28px;
    }

    .site-footer .shell {
      border-radius: 5px;
      min-height: 68px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 18px;
      padding: 0 22px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.16em;
    }

    @media (max-width: 1120px) {
      .hero-grid,
      .section-head,
      .upload-panel {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .hero-copy,
      .terminal {
        min-height: auto;
      }

      .grid-4 { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
      .grid-3,
      .stat-band { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
    }

    @media (max-width: 760px) {
      .nav { display: none; }

      .hero-metrics,
      .grid-3,
      .grid-4,
      .stat-band,
      .input-row,
      .upload-panel {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .tip {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        gap: 8px;
      }

      .site-header .shell,
      .site-footer .shell {
        border-radius: 5px;
        min-height: auto;
        padding-top: 16px;
        padding-bottom: 16px;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: flex-start;
      }

      h1 { max-width: 100%; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header class="site-header">
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="shell glass">
        <a href="#" class="brand">
          <span class="brand-mark" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          <span>FUCK.REPAIR</span>
        </a>

        <nav class="nav">
          <a href="#mission">Mission</a>
          <a href="#manuals">Manuals</a>
          <a href="#tips">Tips</a>
          <a href="#upload">Upload</a>
          <a href="#join">Join</a>
        </nav>

        <a class="button" href="#upload">Upload Manual</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main>
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="wrap">
        <div class="hero-grid">
          <div class="hero-copy glass">
            <div>
              <div class="eyebrow">Universal repair archive</div>
              <h1>IF IT'S BROKEN, START HERE.</h1>

              <p class="hero-sub">
                FUCK.repair is a universal repair platform for manuals, diagnostics, field notes, and real-world fix methods.
                Appliance. Pump. Laptop. Gate motor. Pool heater. Dirt bike. Dishwasher. Whatever it is, the instinct should become automatic:
                broken thing = FUCK.repair.
              </p>

              <div class="hero-actions">
                <a class="button primary" href="#join">Get Early Access</a>
                <a class="button" href="#upload">Upload a Manual</a>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="hero-metrics">
              <div class="metric">
                <span class="metric-kicker">Manual Library</span>
                <strong>Users upload manuals for everyone's benefit.</strong>
              </div>
              <div class="metric">
                <span class="metric-kicker">Repair Notes</span>
                <strong>Tips and tricks for absolutely anything.</strong>
              </div>
              <div class="metric">
                <span class="metric-kicker">Brand Recall</span>
                <strong>Fastest path from frustration to action.</strong>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <aside class="hero-side">
            <div class="panel glass terminal">
              <div class="terminal-top">
                <span>Live concept feed</span>
                <span>Precision / archive / field reality</span>
              </div>
              <div class="terminal-body">
                <span class="terminal-line"><span class="prompt">></span> USER ISSUE: washer stops mid-cycle</span>
                <span class="terminal-line muted">checking: drain path / lid switch / board fault / pressure sensor</span>
                <span class="terminal-line ok">result: start with lid switch and clogged filter before replacing control board</span>
                <br />
                <span class="terminal-line"><span class="prompt">></span> USER ISSUE: salt cell not generating</span>
                <span class="terminal-line muted">checking: flow switch / scale load / salinity / amp draw / temp lockout</span>
                <span class="terminal-line ok">result: verify actual salinity and inspect scale before buying new cell</span>
                <br />
                <span class="terminal-line"><span class="prompt">></span> USER ISSUE: garage door hums but won't move</span>
                <span class="terminal-line muted">checking: capacitor / travel lock / trolley bind / spring failure</span>
                <span class="terminal-line ok">result: broken spring likely — stop running opener until spring is addressed</span>
                <br />
                <span class="terminal-line"><span class="prompt">></span> USER ISSUE: laptop thermal throttling</span>
                <span class="terminal-line muted">checking: fan blockage / dried paste / background load / bios profile</span>
                <span class="terminal-line ok">result: clean fins, verify fan RPM, then repaste if temps stay high</span>
                <br />
                <span class="terminal-line"><span class="prompt">></span> USER ISSUE: unknown machine, no manual</span>
                <span class="terminal-line muted">searching community archive...</span>
                <span class="terminal-line ok">result: 3 similar manuals found + 2 field notes + 1 teardown guide</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </aside>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section" id="mission">
      <div class="wrap">
        <div class="section-card glass">
          <div class="section-head">
            <h2>Repair knowledge should feel inevitable, not buried.</h2>
            <div class="section-intro">
              Most things are not difficult to fix. They are difficult to diagnose clearly. The internet is full of bad guesses,
              dead links, vague forum replies, and generic filler. FUCK.repair is built around a cleaner model: manuals that stay available,
